xplain intent, short enough to remain scannable.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2} --><h2>Strengthen Mission Trust</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>Use a structured mission narrative to increase supporter confidence.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:buttons --><div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"backgroundColor\":\"brand\"} --><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-brand-background-color has-background wp-element-button\">Request Demo</a></div><!-- /wp:button --><!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-outline\"} --><div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">Contact Team</a></div><!-- /wp:button --></div><!-- /wp:buttons --><!-- /wp:group --></div>"
